Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:29.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:34.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:36.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:41.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:44.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:50.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:54.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:02.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:07.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:12.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:18.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:23.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:30.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:35.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:40.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:46.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:51.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:29.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}爱太过沉重而拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:34.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}由爱生恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:36.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}任何事都是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:41.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}尴尬的事由总被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:44.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}这伪善者的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}在扭曲的泥沼时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:50.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}本已约定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:54.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也不觉擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:02.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}彼此伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}抛开原有的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:07.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}莫非这就是末路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:12.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不认同命运 奋起反抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:18.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也无法逃离坠落时的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:23.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}Ah 多少次我都能寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:30.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你的瞳眸 温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:33.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}「爱永远只能给我伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:35.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:40.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}是否曾因害怕相信而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}承认脆弱 变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:46.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不再畏惧 努力相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:51.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}定能找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在4年前阿撒迪斯坦内乱时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接触过天人的成员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那时的事我早在4年前就说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今时不同往日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今Gundam新机型的出现 再次使你成为焦点人物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦王国第一皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:02:02.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(264,299)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}阿勒路亚营救作战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议会已经通过了将联邦保安局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,划为独立治安维持部队的直辖组织的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4千万人规模的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够创设成功全靠Veda的情报统制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能尽微薄之力是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府不能放任任何微弱的抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了即将来临的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待着你们的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正是为此而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忠实地执行着伊欧利亚·舒恩伯格的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的只有我们 变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦的公主 之前一直都置之不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么改变主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知故问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那里也有Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来 实验体E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个人吗 在这监狱被关押了4年的Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不受我脑量子波的干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然报告中说原因是头部受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然还活着 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊  在Home一直和你说话的阿勒路亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:53.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这里的Home，指超人机关对少年实验品进行培养的场所）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫什么玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:04:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你就是玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(365,367)}拉格朗日1  资源卫星群
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS战斗经验呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是开过作业用的工程机械
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带了个彻底的外行人回来吗 刹那那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不是有很多事要做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的教官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔·狄兰提
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 Arios和Cherudim的收容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还关在房里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚称她没回归天人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确和记录里一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne和我们是从不同立场进行武力介入的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说你们不是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 你们也一样用Gundam杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使别人有和我一样的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的所作所为必然招来仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界明明很和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安乐的日子本来可以继续
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们毁了我的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要自己和平就好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 谁都不想遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 转属到A-LAWS后有什么异常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是训练量比平常多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 超人机关的相关资料里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有叫玛丽这名字的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽? 不 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没收的资料我应该都看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有任务  失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 主力部队已抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一收到联络 全员便各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照任务计划 布下警戒态势
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.54,0:06:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系先行部队的比利斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带翼机的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被监禁在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给上层后就毫无音讯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS却知道此事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如Level 2的情报所述
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认Meister生存
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS也聚过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来应对 你可以回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 为什么改了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那言行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不同人格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美发来暗号通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人革联反政府势力收监设施里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现阿勒路亚·哈普提森
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那个人 他是Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被联邦抓住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 召集全员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开战术会议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 找到阿勒路亚了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚?谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴 同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何中止Gundam的搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那个必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部好像对天人下了诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对不起地面部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是个了解对方战力的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的找到阿勒路亚了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是王留美的确定情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来开始救援作战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援 怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你来策划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇·李·诺列嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我们战术预报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他若能回来 就能进行Gundam四机的作战行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此我心里照样没底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助我们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了救出阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐 给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把期待都推给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的预报 改变不了任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会置大家于危险的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使任务失败 也不会归咎于你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无论做什么 都要救出阿勒路亚 救出同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我们战术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德 待会能把现场战力和环境数据告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美发来了详细数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 连被监禁的人名和地点都有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要抑制这架空母的粒子光束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 莱尔·狄兰提的能力值竟如此之高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}00 Seravee Cherudim 出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:07.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}所有的Meister请乘上所属高达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要实战了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为你有出场的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我倒轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内好像很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:12.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第一 第二甲板电力供给转为战斗模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:15.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}托勒密残余粒子率85%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出同伴 救出同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请正在作业的人员撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始 作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee 装备专用火箭炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin Drive虽然启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还很不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要使用TRANS-AM哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐发来了任务计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 这什么计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅300秒的闪电作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是皇·李·诺列嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 也有我的戏份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你支援了 哈罗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特莱玛奥斯 开始大气层突入程序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Seravee Cherudim 出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:12.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Cherudim Gundam：GN-006 智天使高达，Dynames的强化机型）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00：43 开始任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios保持发射状态待机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Arios Gundam：GN-007 堕天使高达，Kyrios的强化机型）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美的报告中监禁阿勒路亚的设施里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔和阿勒路亚在同一设施里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field最大幅度展开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始突入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 轨道柱观测所来电
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到突入大气层的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是运输舰级别的规模
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 宇宙飞船整个降落地面…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备炮击 MS部队也赶快做好出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利斯中尉 敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS机库…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人的宇宙飞船…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不减速? 难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field最大幅度展开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 潜水模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲进海里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌…敌舰潜入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用导弹迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要让粒子光束效果减半吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 提耶利亚 粒子光束的扩散时间大约是300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此期间找到阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3分钟内完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剩下的2分钟再救一个人如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这震动是?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方MS出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 开始炮狙击战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中也无妨 牵制他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 哈罗 哥哥在战斗时都说些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙击 狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim Gundam 洛克昂·史特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙击目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的粒子量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死守这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠近些的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死也不退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 其他方向来的攻击?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 击落敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是新手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了 打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧而已 碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营救队…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给本人 中尉去确保E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 KATARON正在释放囚犯们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天人联手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去这个地点 Arios马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现阿勒路亚了 将Arios…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚好 Arios射出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 再次下潜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GN导弹牵制 同时向汇合地点移动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩余120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚犯们被放出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是刹那他们干的 他们到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是指定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 实验体E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面发生了战斗? 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离门远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩余时间不到30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这种名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这才是你真正的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 玛丽·帕珐西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽·帕珐西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧 E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 阿勒路亚 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽明明就在眼前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽 我一定会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam有三架?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止射击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先确保设施安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam撤离 开始撤退行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成 任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 总算
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同志们都被成功救出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏Gin-1的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳 听了营救部队成员的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一位成员在设施中目击到了阿撒迪斯坦第一皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔殿下的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛…玛莉娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被囚禁了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我们无暇保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但据报告称 玛莉娜公主被疑似天人的成员带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走了? 被天人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:18.63,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}純真さがシンプルな力に変わる時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:23.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:31.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ガラスケースに横たわる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:38.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:42.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}振り上げた手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}落ちるように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:54.76,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}しゃがみこんだ
