Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:21.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这生死一线之间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:27.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}却这样可悲地与我相衬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚 你为什么会被联邦政府抓住?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人机关的情报…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船还真了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还能在水中航行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛…洛克昂 怎么会?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种反应我都看腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.79,0:23:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要勉强改变自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 阿勒路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.31,0:23:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的缘故 你被卷入了额外的麻烦中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 玛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.52,0:23:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你又要去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只此一途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 战斗以外的生活方式还有许多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.99,0:23:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能通过战斗实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样 太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么哭?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你哭不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯下错误的人只能靠自身纠正它
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎罪之旅 同时也是再生之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.86,0:24:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而罪孽不会消失


